      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a really impressive number. Honestly, it's hard to find NGOs that stay that efficient. I've heard some talk in donor circles that administrative and marketing costs for large organizations like Humanitarian Reach can often creep up to 30% or 40%. Is there any breakdown you can show me that explains how you keep it as low as 5%?",
