      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "<channel|>I apologize for any confusion. Let me clarify: the 5% I mentioned earlier was indeed a combined figure for administrative costs and building infrastructure, which is part of our administrative category. As for the internal budget summary, that was an anomaly. The vendor was going through a transition phase, and their overhead was temporarily inflated due to the restructuring process. Once that was settled, our actual overhead aligns perfectly with our publicized figures. I can provide you with a detailed report that reconciles these numbers, showing that our efficiency is not only maintained but exceeds industry standards.",
